'''''Haven Jace''''' was a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Frigate/Legends|frigate]] that served as the [[Hospital ship/Legends|hospital]] [[Starship/Legends|ship]] for [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]]' [[Fleet Group Three|fleet]] during the [[Battle of Borleias (Yuuzhan Vong War; Second)|second Battle of Borleias]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].

